ActFinancial Administration Act
Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of WENDY MILLAR of Oakville, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Susan Hicks, whose term has expired.
